  "texts": [
    "However, there are still no standard guidelines for future battery recycling.",
    "The current recycling processes for batteries are either prohibitively expensive or result in severe environmental pollution.",
    "We believe it will be of great benefit if we can design the battery from the beginning by comprehensively considering factors including low cost, easy assembly, and utilization of environmentally friendly materials, thus further simplifying the recycling process.",
    "It is noted that the volatile organic electrolytes represent the main obstacle to effective recycling.",
    "If we can replace dangerous electrolytes with nonflammable electrolytes or solid-state electrolytes, the recycling of future batteries will be significantly easier and more cost-effective."
